                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ixquieh",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ahpub's twin sister and a former chief. She fought alongside the first Pyro Archon,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7074,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/10/237301566/e7f7eee058f60fc225b1f5bc654a08e0_6006799746535018143.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Xbalanque",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", and later defended the Saurians from her brother and",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7296,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Och-Kan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "'s orders. She was killed by her brother.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Sakkuk",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A peacemaker and one of the six heroes who defeated the ruler of the Cinder City.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7492,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/24/237301566/635c5399fafe1d44199f06a2bf16c6d4_7800839300009312366.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Sundjatta",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A former chief who went with Tenoch to the future Mare Jivari during the",
                      "type": "text"
