                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Traore",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Legendary Elder of the Children of Echoes who fought along with the warriors from",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4811,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_7086984801760748.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Khaenri'ah",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "during the Cataclysm 500 years ago. According to a legend, Traore defeated the Volcano Lord with the Shadow Pins.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
