                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/31/237301566/60094afc2111c06296aee0d8612ef2fd_6097913331375178884.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "August 17, 2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The warriors in the Stadium of the Sacred Flame are about to enter the fray.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "While waiting for the competition to begin,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Why not take some time to listen to our three friends share the various facets of their tribal lives?",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Kachina's Notes: \"Natlan's Saurian Companions\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/31/237301566/65b1403954ff9fc25946aec7ec525a94_6773493571863860084.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "August 28, 2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "You'll run into all kinds of Saurians during your adventures here in Natlan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Journey alongside the Saurians and immerse yourself in the breathtaking vistas of Natlan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
